data.text:
'High School Musical’ first premiered on the Disney Channel back in 2006 and became a phenomenon that made stars of Zac Efron, Vanessa Hudgens and Ashley Tisdale and spawned two sequels, a spin-off and a television show.

But how much do you know about the smash hit franchise?

A Kensington Palace insider has claimed that Kate Middleton will indefinitely be stepping back from public duties again, after last being seen at Wimbledon.
